WITH lagged_data AS (
  SELECT
    TIMESTAMP(tmstp) as time,
    m_visits,
    LAG(m_visits) OVER (ORDER BY tmstp) as prev_m_visits,
    LAG(TIMESTAMP(tmstp)) OVER (ORDER BY tmstp) as pre_timestamp
  FROM
    `Piano.total_visits_today_append`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "$LRA"
        AND page_chapter1 = "$Redaktionen_mapped"
        AND page_chapter2 = "$Unterkapitel"
        AND sendungs_id = "$Sendung"
    AND date >= ${bq_timeframe_start:doublequote} AND date <= ${bq_timeframe_end:doublequote} --$Zeitraum 
    AND source != "mdr_app"
    AND 
    CASE "$LRA"
    WHEN "ndr.de" THEN True
    WHEN "eurovision.de" THEN True
    ELSE (
      CASE "$Redaktionen_mapped"
        WHEN "Brisant" THEN origin = "sendung"
        WHEN "Jump" THEN origin = "sendung"
        WHEN "Sputnik" THEN origin = "sendung"
        WHEN "Alle Kapitel 1" THEN origin = "sendung"
        WHEN "klassik" THEN origin = "klassik"
        WHEN "sorbisches-programm" THEN origin = "serbski"
        ELSE True
      END
    )
    END
    ORDER by time DESC
    ${lim}
    -- 09:00     --> 09:20. --- > 09:30

),
min_time_from_base AS (
  -- This with statement will used in order to find out which is the last valid upload(e.g. the one with valid successor)
  SELECT MIN(pre_timestamp) min_time FROM lagged_data
  WHERE TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) > 10
), 
max_time_from_base AS (
    -- THis with statement will be used if no gap exists
    SELECT MAX(time) as max_time FROM lagged_data
    WHERE TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) = 10
),
cleaned_lagged_data AS (
  SELECT * from lagged_data 
  WHERE
  time <= (SELECT COALESCE( min_time_from_base.min_time, max_time_from_base.max_time )
  FROM max_time_from_base, min_time_from_base)
),
daily_data AS (
  SELECT
     TIMESTAMP(date, "Europe/Berlin") as time,
    TIMESTAMP_SUB(TIMESTAMP(date,  "Europe/Berlin"), INTERVAL 10 MINUTE) as pre_timestamp,
    m_visits as visits_past_5_minutes_adjusted,
    "${type}" as type, "${Zeitraumlabels:text}" as refId
  FROM
    `Piano.total_visits${feverCurveDataset:raw}`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "$LRA"
    AND page_chapter1 = "$Redaktionen_mapped"
    AND page_chapter2 = "$Unterkapitel"
    AND sendungs_id = "$Sendung"
    AND date >= ${bq_timeframe_start:doublequote} AND date <= ${bq_timeframe_end:doublequote}--$Zeitraum
    ORDER BY time DESC
),
adjusted_lagged_data AS (
  SELECT
    DATE_SUB(time, INTERVAL 2 hour) as time,
    DATE_SUB(pre_timestamp, INTERVAL 2 hour) as pre_timestamp,
    -- Calculate time difference in minutes
    TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) as time_diff,
    -- Adjust visits count based on time difference
    CASE
      WHEN FALSE AND TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) > 10 OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) < 0 AND "${Glaettung:text}" = "Glätten" THEN
        (m_visits - prev_m_visits) / TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) * 10
      ELSE
        m_visits - prev_m_visits
    END as visits_past_5_minutes_adjusted,
    "${type}" as type, 
    "${Zeitraumlabels:text}" as refId
  FROM
    cleaned_lagged_data
)
SELECT
  TIMESTAMP_ADD(time, INTERVAL 1 SECOND) as time,
  TIMESTAMP_ADD(pre_timestamp, INTERVAL 1 SECOND) as pre_timestamp,
  MAX(ROUND(visits_past_5_minutes_adjusted)) as visits_past_5_minutes,
  type,
  refId,
   "${Glaettung:text}" as glaettung,
   "Zeitraum" as zeitraum
FROM
  ${dataset}
WHERE
  visits_past_5_minutes_adjusted IS NOT NULL
  AND visits_past_5_minutes_adjusted > 0
  AND TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, MINUTE) = 10 OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(time, pre_timestamp, HOUR) = 1
  GROUP BY time, pre_timestamp, type, refId
ORDER BY
  time ASC
  ${lim}

CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"

  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "last_hour"
  ELSE "daily"
  END

SELECT CASE "$App"
WHEN "NDR Schleswig-Holstein" THEN "NDR SH"
WHEN "NDR Hamburg" THEN "NDR HH"
WHEN "NDR Mecklenburg-Vorpommern" THEN "NDR MV"
WHEN "NDR Elbphilharmonie Orchester" THEN "Elbphilharmonie"
WHEN "NDR Niedersachsen" THEN "NDR NDS"
WHEN "MDR Sachsen-Anhalt" THEN "MDR ST"
WHEN "Sport im Osten" THEN "MDR SPIO"
WHEN  "MDR Sachsen-Anhalt" THEN "MDR ST"
ELSE "$App"
END

CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "today"
  ELSE "daily"
  END

  CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "Heute"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN "Gestern"
  WHEN "Gestern" THEN "Gestern vor 7 Tagen"
  WHEN "Letztes Wochenende" THEN "Vorletztes Wochenende"
  WHEN "Letzte 7 Tage" THEN "Letzte 8-14 Tage"
  WHEN "Letzte 30 Tage" THEN "Letzte 31-60 Tage"
  END

SELECT 
CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "_last_hour"
  END
Select a.LRA  FROM(SELECT DISTINCT LRA FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles`) as a ORDER BY ( CASE WHEN a.LRA like  LEFT('${__user.login}',3) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) DESC

SELECT distinct app FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
WHERE LRA = "$LRA"
ORDER BY app ASC

SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN "$LRA" = 'MDR' THEN (
      SELECT
        distinct product_app_name
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
      WHERE
        app = "$App"
    )
    WHEN "$LRA" = 'NDR' THEN (
      SELECT
        distinct site_level2
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
      WHERE
        app = "$App"
    )
  END

SELECT CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
     WHEN "Gestern" THEN  DATE(DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 DAY))
     WHEN "Heute" THEN  DATE(CURRENT_DATE)
      WHEN "Heute -7d" THEN DATE(CURRENT_DATE)
      ELSE DATE(2000,1,1)
     END

query.rawSql:
SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte Stunde" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', today)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Heute" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', today)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Heute -7d" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', today)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Gestern" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', yesterday)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letztes Wochenende" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', last_saturday)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte 7 Tage" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', interval_7_day)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte 30 Tage" THEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', interval_30_day)
    ELSE FORMAT_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', today)
  END AS relevant_value
FROM `grafana.current_date`

list.name: Zeitraum

options.value: date >= (SELECT saturday FROM(SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY) as saturday)) AND date <= (SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY) as sunday)
date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL  7 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()
date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL  30 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()

list.query: Letzte Stunde : CAST(tmstp AS DATE) = CURRENT_DATE(),    Heute : date = CURRENT_DATE,  Heute -7d : date = CURRENT_DATE(), Gestern : date = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  1 DAY), Letztes Wochenende :  date >= (SELECT saturday FROM(SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY) as saturday)) AND date <= (SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY) as sunday), Letzte 7 Tage : date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  7 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE(), Letzte 30 Tage : date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  30 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()

current.text: DATETIME_DIFF((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time), tmstp, MINUTE) <=70 AND tmstp <= ((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time))
current.value: DATETIME_DIFF((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time), tmstp, MINUTE) <=70 AND tmstp <= ((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time))

query.rawSql:
SELECT 
CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN  " EXTRACT(Hour from tmstp) <= ((SELECT EXTRACT(HOUR FROM max_tmstp) from min_time))"
  WHEN "Heute -7d" THEN  " EXTRACT(Hour from tmstp) <= ((SELECT EXTRACT(HOUR FROM max_tmstp) from min_time))"
  WHEN "Gestern" THEN  "EXTRACT(Hour from tmstp) <= 24"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "DATETIME_DIFF((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time), tmstp, MINUTE) <=70 AND tmstp <= ((SELECT min_tmstp FROM min_time))"
  ELSE "True"
  END
